1 CONT Source Description
1 CONT
1 CONT This database details those persons enumerated in the 1810 United 
1 CONC States Federal Census, the Third Census of the United States. In 
1 CONC addition, the names of those listed on the population schedule are 
1 CONC linked to the actual images of the 1810 Federal Census. Enumerators of 
1 CONC the 1810 census were asked to include the following categories in the 
1 CONC census: name of head of household, number of free white males and 
1 CONC females, number of other free persons except Indians, number of 
1 CONC slaves, town or district and county of residence. Learn more...
